function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	
	-- disable pre RTC elias + taissa + bubble 
	Hydra.ActorDisable(actorEliasPreRTC)
	Hydra.ActorDisable(actorTaissaPreRTC)
	
	Hydra.ActorDisable(actorAndarielSandStorm)
	
	-- disable sandstorm blockers
	for i, actorID in pairs(tSandstormBlockers) do
		Hydra.ActorDisable(actorID)
	end

end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	
	Hydra.ActorClearAnimSetOverride(actorLorath)
	Hydra.ActorClearAnimSetOverride(actorDonan)
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convArgument, idActor, actorLorath)
	Hydra.QActorWait(actorTaissa, 4)
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(actorTaissa)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorTaissa, locTaissaPrefight, "NPC_Walk_Fast", false)
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(actorTaissa, "NPC_Idle_Stand_Exhausted")
end

function Start(flGameTime)
	if bSandstorming then
		for i, actorID in pairs(Hydra.PlayerActorsInLevelArea("Kehj_Forsaken_Chapel")) do
			Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(powerSandstorm, "MAIN", actorID)
		end
	end
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	
	Hydra.ActorDisable(actorNeyrelle)
	bSandstorming = true
	
	Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(actorLorath, animsetLorathSandstorm, false)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorLorath, locLorathPostConv)
	
	Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(actorDonan, animsetDonanSandstorm, false)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorDonan, locDonanPostConv)
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	
	Hydra.ActorDisable(actorTaissa)
	
	Hydra.WeatherOverride(WORLD_THIS, WEATHER_SANDSTORM)
	
	-- enable pre RTC elias + taissa + bubble 
	Hydra.ActorEnable(actorEliasPreRTC)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(actorTaissaPreRTC)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(actorNeyrellePostConvo)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(actorAndarielSandStorm)
	
	for i, actorID in pairs(tSandstormBlockers) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(actorID)
	end
end

WEATHER_SANDSTORM = Hydra.ReferenceWeather("weather_kehjistan_andariel_sandstorm")
WORLD_THIS = Hydra.ReferenceWorld("Sanctuary_Eastern_Continent")
bSandstorming = false
Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(actorAndarielSandStorm, 8)

Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(actorLorath, animsetLorathIntro)
Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(actorDonan, animsetDonanIntro)
